7.title: El mejor regalo del mundo

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

7.plot: Jesus gives Inspector Torres the exact place where the loaded drug boat will enter. The police will complete the operation against drug trafficking, although he will not be able to capture Duque and his associates, who have enough time to escape. Unable to capture the drug traffickers, Inspector Torres begins to think that there is a mole inside his team that has passed the information to the drug gang so they can escape.

8.title: Una nueva vida

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

8.plot: Duke remains hidden in Colombia with Morón and Cardona. After the failure of the operation, the bosses of the band do not trust him and subject him to a hard test to show that he is on his side. Meanwhile, Vanesa and Cristina do not know what to do since Jessica and the drug traffickers left the neighborhood. The first took refuge in the world of drugs, while Cris tries to take his first steps in interpretation. In addition, Torres goes to therapy in order to find out the cause of his obsessions.

9.title: Cata en el espejo

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

9.plot: Catalina recovers from her operation, but the woman shown by the mirror is not the one she ever had known. The difficult personal situation he goes through makes her looks for support in Jessica, the least indicated person to help her. Duque, meanwhile, prepares his return to Spain, as the relationship with the Colombian cartel is increasingly complicated, while inspector Torres tries to show that a "mole" within the police body dismantled the operation.

10.title: Statu quo

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

10.plot: Duque is cautious after his return to Spain. His goal is to seal an agreement that will make him someone very important in drug trafficking, but first he must take care of expelling Buco and his followers from the neighborhood. On the other hand, Fina discovers that the dresses she designed for Tomás are for sale without her permission.

11.title: El precio del poder

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

11.plot: Duque starts a new operation. This time, the drug trafficker will introduce a drug shipment using the contacts of Cortés, his new partner and the man he has left Catalina for. On the other hand, happiness reaches Fina's home: the relationship between her and Tomás goes on, she has left the job as operator to devote herself completely to fashion design and has reunited with her daughter. In addition, a new inspector - agent Cuesta - joins Torres' group, while Jesús and Paula make their relationship public. Cristina continues her career as an actress in erotic movies.

12.title: Cita con la muerte

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

12.plot: The life of Jesus is in danger after the shot he received from Pertur. Catalina's brother, seriously injured, is torn between life and death in the hospital surrounded by his family and friends. The grave situation of Jesus reunites mother and daughter, who mourn inconsolably before the young man's bed. Fina has the unconditional support of Tomás, but Catalina feels alone and begins to believe that Duque is responsible for the situation in which his brother is. On the other hand, Inspector Torres believes that behind the shot that wounded Jesus are the hands of Duque....

1.title: La función debe continuar

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

1.plot: Two months have passed since Jesus died, but the wounds are still open. Fina just wants to forget her daughter Catalina, whom she considers guilty of all the ills of the family. Although it seems difficult to find a solution, the young woman is determined to correct the mistakes she made in the past. After the proposal of Miguel Cortés to marry her, Catalina will weigh the consequences that would bring the link with the employer: on the one hand, it seems the best way to make Rafael Duque pay what he did, but on the other, neither love, nor Even ambition, move her to ...

2.title: Da svidania! (Hasta la vista)

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

2.plot: Despite having mixed feelings, Catalina does not renounce her revenge against Rafael Duque. With the collaboration of Martínez, Cortés' lawyer, the young woman tries to get her husband to lose confidence in the drug trafficker. For her part, Paula, who is deeply affected by the death of Jesus, confesses to her friend Catalina that she is pregnant and asks for money to have an abortion. Faced with this situation, Cata goes to his mother to help convince Paula to have the child, but Fina despises her and throws her out of the house. After meditating, the mother of the ...

3.title: Amigos bajo tierra

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

3.plot: The wishes of Rafael Duque seem to be closer to being fulfilled. Thanks to the collaboration of Catalina, Cortés will be separated from the treatment that the young drug trafficker maintains with the Russian mafia. This help is considered by Duke as an act of commitment and reconciliation with his beloved, although the real intention of Catherine is another. On the other hand, the appearance of Vladimir's corpse will complicate the agreement between the Duke and Anatoly, a business in which Cortés is not willing to be left out. More worried about his professional life...

4.title: Se derramarán más lágrimas

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

4.plot: Jessica discovers that Catalina and Rafael Duque are seeing each other secretly, a fact that will provoke mixed feelings in the young woman. After considering what is best for her, she decides to get away from the drug trafficker. On the other hand Anatoly, encouraged by Martinez, decides to ask for an advance to Duque of 3% of what was agreed, that is, one million euros. The henchmen of the drug trafficker must raise the money in three days, so they will plan the theft of luxury cars.

5.title: La ratonera

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

5.plot: Miguel Cortés, moved by jealousy, orders the murder of Duke. Jessica, who suspects what the businessman's intentions are, decides to talk to Catalina. Despite her doubts, the young woman will end up trusting her friend and will try to prevent Duque from feeling that his life is in danger. On the other hand, Agustín is victim of a shooting, fact that seems a signal of revenge of Anatoly by the murder of Vladimir. For the good of the business, Rafael Duque has no choice but to rely on the oath of innocence of the head of the Russian mafia. Cortés will be in charge of ...

6.title: Huellas en la arena

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

6.plot: Threatened by those who were accomplices of his business and knowing that he is in a difficult situation, Duque will try to regain his position at the helm of his business. Catalina is also aware that she is on a tightrope. After trying to finish with Duke, he knows that his evil plan can not go unpunished.

7.title: La naturaleza del escorpión

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

7.plot: Duque must carry out the first mission commissioned by the inspectors Torres y Cuesta, after agreeing to collaborate with the police. Although he runs the risk of losing the trust of his allies, the young drug trafficker agrees motivated by his desire to recover Catherine. On the other hand, Fina's daughter begins to doubt the decisions she has made. He seems to have understood that there is no point in continuing with Miguel Cortés, but he knows that it will not be easy to take the step of abandoning him. Catalina wonders if it is a good idea to go back to Rafael, so...

8.title: La educación sentimental

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

8.plot: Cortés and Duque decide to postpone the solution to their differences until they conclude the business they have in common with Anatoly. However, Catalina will receive her punishment immediately: her husband kidnaps Paula to show him that he is capable of anything. Meanwhile, Rafael is convinced that his relationship with Catalina is getting cold, forcing Torres to support him before the young woman. Although Duque's men stand by his side, they are unhappy with his boss's new white glove style and start to get impatient. After losing the confidence of her clients ...

10.title: Canciones tristes

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

10.plot: Catalina is hospitalized recovering from the fainting she suffered in the nightclub. This circumstance prevents the young woman from transmitting to Duque information of vital importance that would serve to dismantle her husband's business. Concerned about Catalina's state of health, Rafael tries by all means to distance her from Cortés. However, it is not an easy task since Inspector Torres decides to keep an eye on the drug trafficker so that he does not attack his enemy and thus explode the police operation in which they have been working for so long. Meanwhile, ...

11.title: Cata sobre sábanas de seda

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

11.plot: Catalina prepares her escape with Duke. Given the unforeseen circumstances that arise, the young drug trafficker must change his forced plan to end with Cortes. The key is still Mr. Martínez. With the help of Torres, they manage to demonstrate to Cortes' assistant that the sect to which his daughter belongs is financed by his own boss. This information comes to Martinez before telling Cortes that he has discovered the relationship between Duque and the police.

12.title: Secretos y mentiras

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

12.plot: Cortés is willing to find out who is betraying him, since he has the help of the Commissioner. All the clues lead him to Martinez who, after discovering that the sect in which his daughter finds himself is financed by Cortés, will not hesitate to supply Duque with the information he needs to imprison his boss. Meanwhile, the young drug trafficker prepares the flight of his beloved, who is no longer under the influence of drugs. Despite being in a better state, Catalina knows that if she continues at her husband's side, her life is in danger. On the other hand, Torres,...

13.title: Plata o plomo

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

13.plot: Martinez is in the hospital struggling between life and death, so Duque is aware that the only way to save Catalina, captive in a secret place in the house waiting for its end, is to kill Cortés. The drug trafficker goes to his enemy's house to fulfill his purpose. However, Morón awaits at the doors surrounded by armed bodyguards. In addition, before the imminence of the Russian-Colombian exchange, Torres gives the order so that the assault to the ships takes place.

14.title: Viaje al final de la noche

episode of.title: Sin tetas no hay paraíso (TV Series 2008–2009)

14.plot: Duque and Catalina can not carry out their plan of escape, since Morón has their passports and Duque's money. The young man can not imagine that his allies Gitano and Pertur have gone over to the Colombian side and are looking for him to kill him. Finally, Gitano saves the life of his boss, who has prepared a trap, and asks Moron for Duque's money in exchange for his head. In addition, Paula prematurely gives birth to a child who decides to call Jesus. Meanwhile, Cristina sees how Pancho and Gustavo make her two proposals in which her future is at stake and Vanesa ...
